==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Independence Day
<hw>In`de*pend"ence Day</hw>. <def>In the United States, a holiday, the
4th of July, commemorating the adoption of the Declaration of
Independence on that day in 1776.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Independency</ent>⟦br⟧
